<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Resumint</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
      padding: 50px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .emoji {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .feature {
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .feature h3 {
      margin: 10px 0 5px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .feature p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .credit-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .credit-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #92400e;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background: #f9fafb;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #3b82f6;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://xerothermic-beige-i5tbo3rmdi.edgeone.dev/resumint.png" alt="{{appName}}" style="height: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
      <h1>Welcome to {{appName}}!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi {{name}}! üëã</h2>
      
      <p>We're thrilled to have you join the {{appName}} community! You're now part of thousands of professionals creating stunning resumes and portfolios with AI-powered tools.</p>
      
      <div class="credit-box">
        <h3>‚ú® Your Welcome Gift</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #92400e; margin: 0;">
          <strong>10 Free Credits</strong> to get you started!
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">Here's what you can do with {{appName}}:</h3>
      
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üìÑ</div>
          <h3>AI Resume Builder</h3>
          <p>Create ATS-optimized resumes in minutes</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üåê</div>
          <h3>Portfolio Websites</h3>
          <p>Publish stunning portfolio sites</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">‚ö°</div>
          <h3>AI Enhancement</h3>
          <p>Improve content with AI suggestions</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üìä</div>
          <h3>Resume Scoring</h3>
          <p>Get detailed ATS compatibility scores</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <center>
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard ‚Üí</a>
      </center>
      
      <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">Quick Start Guide:</h3>
      <ol style="color: #4b5563;">
        <li>Choose a beautiful template</li>
        <li>Fill in your details or import from LinkedIn</li>
        <li>Let AI enhance your content</li>
        <li>Download or publish your resume/portfolio</li>
      </ol>
      
      <p>Need help getting started? Check out our <a href="{{appUrl}}/docs" style="color: #3b82f6;">documentation</a> or reach out to our support team.</p>
      
      <p>
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The {{appName}} Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{appUrl}}">Website</a> | 
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/docs">Documentation</a> | 
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/support">Support</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
